job_text:
We are looking for a highly skilled and experienced Senior Python Developer with expertise in Natural Language Processing (NLP) to join our team. You will be responsible for developing a chatbot using an open API model, specifically GPT-4. The chatbot should not only provide accurate responses but also have the capability to recommend options to our customers based on their preferences and requirements. This is an exciting opportunity to work on an innovative project that will enhance our customer experience and streamline our business operations.

Responsibilities:
- Collaborate with the team to understand project requirements and objectives
- Design, develop, and deploy a chatbot using Python and an open API like GPT-4
- Implement NLP techniques and algorithms to enable intelligent conversation flows and accurate responses
- Develop recommendation algorithms to suggest relevant options to customers based on their preferences and requirements
- Integrate the chatbot with existing systems and platforms, ensuring seamless functionality
- Optimize and fine-tune the chatbot's performance through testing, debugging, and improvement iterations
- Stay up to date with the latest advancements in NLP and recommendation systems and implement best practices
- Document code, processes, and project updates to ensure knowledge sharing within the team

Requirements:
- Proven experience as a Senior Python Developer, preferably with expertise in NLP and recommendation systems
- Strong knowledge of Python programming language and related frameworks (e.g., Flask, Django)
- Solid understanding of NLP concepts, algorithms, and libraries (e.g., NLTK, spaCy)
- Experience in developing chatbots or conversational AI applications using open API models (e.g., GPT-4)
- Familiarity with machine learning techniques and libraries (e.g., scikit-learn, TensorFlow)
- Experience in building recommendation systems using collaborative filtering, content-based filtering, or other relevant techniques
- Proficiency in working with RESTful APIs and integrating third-party services
- Strong problem-solving and analytical skills, with a keen eye for detail
- Excellent communication and collaboration abilities
- Bachelor's or Master's degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or a related field

Preferred Skills:
- Experience with cloud platforms like AWS or Azure for deployment and scalability
- Knowledge of front-end technologies (HTML, CSS, JavaScript) for chatbot interface customization
- Familiarity with version control systems (e.g., Git) and Agile development methodologies
